title: Jungle Boys Ocala
cleaned_text:
COVID-19 vaccination cards are not required for entry.

In order to enter the facility, ALL Medical Patients and/or Caregivers must present an active medical marijuana registry ID and valid ID card (driver’s license or government issued ID).

Parking is available on either side of the store and out front. *Please note that Jungle Boys Florida is not responsible for theft or damage to vehicles.
